    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Drawing on the deepest fears of a group of creatures, you create illusory creatures in their minds, visible only to them. Each creature in a 30-foot-radius sphere centered on a point of your choice within range must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature becomes &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] for the duration. The illusion calls on the creature's deepest fears, manifesting its worst nightmares as an implacable threat. At the end of each of the &amp;Reference[condition=frightened] creature's turns, it must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or take [[/damage 4d10 type=psychic]] damage. On a successful save, the spell ends for that creature.</p></div>",
